 Matters, in this piece, writes about Sunday Adeyemo, A.K.A. Sunday Igboho. January 25, 2021 In "Viewpoint" Debunks rumour of reprisal attack Ibadan-based influential man, Chief Sunday Adeyemo, popularly known as Sunday Igboho, has broken silence over the death of one of his aides, Ebenezer Abiola, who was attacked by suspected gunmen and killed in cold blood at Oke Fia, Osogbo, Osun State, weeks ago, and also… July 3, 2019 In "News"